synopsis: When a sudden flood traps a group of strangers in an outback roadhouse it becomes clear that the threat from within the group is far greater than from raging torrent outside.
casting: ['John Jarratt', 'Craig McLachlan', 'Charlie Jarratt', 'Jessica Napier', 'Sacha Horler', 'Chris Haywood']

synopsis: The world is under attack by an alien armada led by the powerful Apokoliptian, Darkseid. A group of superheroes consisting of Superman, Batman, Wonder Woman, The Flash, Green Lantern, Cyborg, and Shazam must set aside their differences and gather together to defend Earth.
tagline: A time when heroes became legends.
